hopobject.body: Could I have an application form? medlabgear.com With this as her introduction, bean collecting and growing became an obsession and Caroline now has ‘Gigantes’ from the southern Mediterranean, pea beans from West Dean (beautiful cream and deep red bicolour beans), black and white from Slovenia, dark red ones from Mexico, borlotti beans of three types, all from Italy, as well haricots, navy beans, flageolet beans, black, shiny Cherokee “Trail of Tears” beans (so called because the Cherokee tribe took the beans with them when they were thrown off their land), and some brown and white ones, which are particularly creamy, soft and delicious, from Croatia.
